      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for hemolysis prediction must meet SQA level 4: documented version control, regression testing suite, and independent code review for all hemolysis-relevant modules.",
      "rationale": "CFD solver has version control and basic unit tests but lacks an independent code review for the hemolysis damage accumulation module. Achieved SQA level 2 only; gap of 2 levels at MRL 5 is unacceptable."
    },
