      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions must confirm expected convergence rates for all governing equations including the hemolysis transport equation.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy study was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not extended to the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Achieved level 2; required level 4 for MRL 5 device."
