      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis damage model (e.g., power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger) must be justified against alternative model forms; model form uncertainty must be quantified and propagated to the hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used; no alternative model forms were evaluated. Model form uncertainty was not quantified. This is the primary epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 2."
